      <title>家乡风景图</title>
      <link href="/posts/ce066d56/"/>
      <url>/posts/ce066d56/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>回老家住了3天，好久没回，变化好大。  </p><h2 id="屋后面的田野"><a href="#屋后面的田野" class="headerlink" title="屋后面的田野"></a>屋后面的田野</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117165947.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117171813.jpg"><br>地里原来种的是枣树，前不久全部挖去了<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117171840.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117171904.jpg"><br>打霜后，焉掉了的庄稼<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172155.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172433.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172527.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172700.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172751.jpg"><br>长久无人居住，被风雨摧残后破败的房子<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172826.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117172847.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173005.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173018.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173033.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173049.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173114.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173131.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173150.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173208.jpg"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zxx-0/picgo/img/20210117173231.jpg">  </p><h2 id="后记"><a href="#后记" class="headerlink" title="后记"></a>后记</h2><p>希望家乡越来越好  </p>]]></content>
      
      
